=head1 DESCRIPTION

The destination information for the metadata table configuration. The
destination table bucket must be in the same Region and Amazon Web
Services account as the general purpose bucket. The specified metadata
table name must be unique within the C<aws_s3_metadata> namespace in
the destination table bucket.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TableArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the metadata table in the metadata
table configuration. The specified metadata table name must be unique
within the C<aws_s3_metadata> namespace in the destination table
bucket.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TableBucketArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the table bucket that's specified as
the destination in the metadata table configuration. The destination
table bucket must be in the same Region and Amazon Web Services account
as the general purpose bucket.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TableName => Str

The name for the metadata table in your metadata table configuration.
The specified metadata table name must be unique within the
C<aws_s3_metadata> namespace in the destination table bucket.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> TableNamespace => Str

The table bucket namespace for the metadata table in your metadata
table configuration. This value is always C<aws_s3_metadata>.



